  "content": " <div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"8965\" class=\"elementor elementor-8965\" data-elementor-settings=\"{&quot;ha_cmc_init_switcher&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\"> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c1fac69 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c1fac69\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-464c7e9\" data-id=\"464c7e9\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb43cb8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"bb43cb8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"6261327459\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9355584 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9355584\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-26a7c5e\" data-id=\"26a7c5e\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46d76c9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"46d76c9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">PREMENSTRUAL SYNDROME </span></h2><blockquote style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Premenstrual syndrome</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> is a </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">group of symptoms both physical and psychological that occur before menstruation</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span></p></blockquote><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Symptoms can range from mild to severe and </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">occur during the luteal phase</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">begin 7-14 days before the onset of menses</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">) and </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">disappear after the onset of menses.</span></p><p> </p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Majority of women experience premenstrual syndrome but it is considered severe if it impairs work, relationships or usual activities.</span></p><h4 style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Causes of Premenstrual Syndrome</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"> </p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The cause of premenstrual syndrome remains </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">unknown/unclear </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">although changes in the hormonal level, Vitamin B6 and calcium deficiency have been suspected.</span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4759814 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4759814\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1c830a0\" data-id=\"1c830a0\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2fc911 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"d2fc911\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"6261327459\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f3c098b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f3c098b\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e79c64d\" data-id=\"e79c64d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-852a799 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"852a799\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"548\" src=\"/images/PREMENSTRUAL-SYNDROME-signs-and-symptoms-1-1024x548.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-8968\" alt=\"PREMENSTRUAL SYNDROME signs and symptoms (1)\" srcset=\"/images/PREMENSTRUAL-SYNDROME-signs-and-symptoms-1-1024x548.jpg 1024w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/PREMENSTRUAL-SYNDROME-signs-and-symptoms-1-600x321.jpg 600w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/PREMENSTRUAL-SYNDROME-signs-and-symptoms-1-300x161.jpg 300w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/PREMENSTRUAL-SYNDROME-signs-and-symptoms-1-768x411.jpg 768w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/PREMENSTRUAL-SYNDROME-signs-and-symptoms-1.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /> </div> </div> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0d1eae elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e0d1eae\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Signs and symptoms of Premenstrual Syndrome</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Premenstrual syndrome presents with both </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">physical </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">and </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">psychological </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">symptoms as outlined below.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Psychological Symptoms</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: These are emotional and mental aspects affected by PMS, including irritability, depression, tension, anxiety, fatigue, and difficulties in concentration.</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Irritability</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Feelings of annoyance, impatience, and mood disturbances.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Depression</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Persistent feelings of sadness, hopelessness, and despair.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tension</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Increased stress levels and heightened emotional response.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Anxiety</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Experiencing nervousness, unease, or a sense of impending doom.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Fatigue</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: A general feeling of tiredness, weakness, and lack of energy.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Inability to Concentrate:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Difficulty focusing, poor attention, and mental fog.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Physical Symptoms</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Physical manifestations of PMS, such as abdominal bloating, perceived weight gain, breast swelling, acne, headache, and migraines.</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Abdominal Bloating:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Swelling or feeling of fullness in the abdominal area.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Feeling of Weight Gain</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Perceived increase in body weight, often due to fluid retention.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Swelling of Breasts</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Breast tenderness and enlargement due to hormonal changes.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Acne</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Skin breakouts and increased oiliness.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Headache</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Pain or discomfort in the head.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Migraine</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Severe headaches often accompanied by other symptoms like nausea and sensitivity to light.</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-dde38ff elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"dde38ff\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-71f454d\" data-id=\"71f454d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dcd9f00 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"dcd9f00\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>  <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"7570414357\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-32234a5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"32234a5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-db881e5\" data-id=\"db881e5\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b35afc4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b35afc4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Management of Premenstrual Syndrome (PMS)</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A woman is considered to have PMS if her symptoms interfere with the activities of daily living.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Non-pharmacological Strategies</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Diet</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Increase intake of vitamin B6, carbohydrates, fruits, and vegetables, such as legumes and cereals.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Avoid consumption of caffeine.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Refrain from smoking and limit alcohol intake.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Reduce overall salt intake.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Educate patients about the benefits of a diet rich in omega-3 fatty acids and low in saturated fats.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Encourage the consumption of fruits and vegetables.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Physical Exercises:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Engage in regular physical activities, including aerobic exercises and walking.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Encourage exercises to relieve bloating, irritability, and insomnia.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Education and Counseling:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Provide education about the causes, treatment, and prevention of PMS.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Offer counselling to address emotional aspects and coping mechanisms.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Stress Management:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Implement relaxation techniques and mental imagery to manage stress.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">General Measures:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Educate the patient about premenstrual syndrome.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Encourage regular exercises to relieve bloating, irritability, and insomnia.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Advise a diet rich in carbohydrates, calcium, omega-3 fatty acids, and low in saturated fats.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Avoid caffeine to reduce breast tenderness and irritability.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Reduce the consumption of sugar, alcohol, and salt.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Restrict salt intake to decrease abdominal bloating and fluid retention.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Encourage the consumption of fruits and vegetables.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Advise patients who smoke to quit.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pharmacological Strategies</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Combined Oral Contraceptives (COCs):</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Use hormonal contraceptives to regulate hormonal fluctuations.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Antidepressants</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: </span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Consider selective serotonin reuptake inhibitors (SSRIs) like fluoxetine (20 mg once daily) or paroxetine (20 mg once daily) if PMS presents with depression and anxiety symptoms.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Start SSRIs at the time of ovulation and stop on the first day of menses.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Monitor for side effects such as insomnia, fatigue, and loss of libido.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Diuretics</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Recommend diuretics, such as furosemide (20-40 mg), for patients with weight gain.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Spironolactone (50-100 mg daily for 7 days) may help reduce fluid retention.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Vitamins</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Consider Vitamin B6 (50-100 mg once daily) and calcium (600 mg twice daily) to reduce physical symptoms.</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5d3bf35 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5d3bf35\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6ade8d6\" data-id=\"6ade8d6\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9cd32ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"9cd32ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"1271890507\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> <!-- .entry-content .clear --> ",
  "semester": "year-1-semester-1"
}